        <h3 class="page-subhead i18n" data-i18n="ftm-about-us-what">What is #findthemasks?</h3>
        <p class="i18n" data-i18n="ftm-about-us-what-details">
          #findthemasks is a global mapping tool and interactive directory for PPE needs. Our mission is to enable
          individuals, communities, makerspace networks, and large-scale manufacturers to engage and assist during the
          COVID-19 pandemic by providing our frontline healthcare and other essential workers with the personal
          protective equipment they need to protect themselves.
        </p>
      </section>
